*Dođeš* li uveče? (Will you come in the evening?)

Bio je veoma uzbuđen kada mu *dođeš* u posetu. (He was very excited when you visited him.)

Kada *dođeš* ću ti dati dar. (When you come, I will give you a gift.)

*Dođeš* li mi pomoći? (Will you come to help me?)

Čekam da *dođeš* još jednom. (I'm waiting for you to come again.)

Kad *dođeš* ćemo se prošetati. (When you come, we will go for a walk.)